hopobject.body: Would you like a receipt? when will generic viagra become available If there is one belief that has united all Americans since the Revolution, it’s that we HATE paying something to get NOTHING. That’s what the Tea Party was all about. All the ObamaCare doomsayers miss this. Would people rather pay even the tiny first year TAX of $95, for which you are guaranteed NOTHING, GUARANTEED, or pay 7-9% of your gross income for something that might be very much worth it or maybe not? I’ll take the later. It’s a slam dunk to me. I HATE PAYING SOMETHING FOR NOTHING!
